(1, 1, '', 'Explore our durable and affordable plastic chairs, ideal for any event or occasion. It\'s built to last, ensuring lasting use without sacrificing quality. With its strong build, it provides reliable seating in any setting. Choose from various stylish designs to match your decor effortlessly. Cleaning is easy, saving you time and effort while keeping your space clean.', 'Cleaning: Use a damp cloth with mild soap to wipe down the chair regularly. Don\'t use strong chemicals or acid-based cleaners as they can damage the plastic. You can also use a dry cloth to wipe it daily.\n-- Handling: When moving the chair, be careful not to push or pull it forcefully.\n-- Storage: If you need to store the chair, you can stack it and keep it together in a room without direct sunlight. \n-- Avoid Sunlight: Keep the chair away from direct sunlight to prevent fading or warping.', '', '', '', ''),
